OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith spells of rain, occasionally
OL,7,Fheavy. Mainly dry this afternoon with
OL,8,Fsome sunshine breaking through, just
OL,9,Fthe odd shower in the northwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mainly dry evening with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. The rest of the
OL,13,Fnight will be generally dry with clear
OL,14,Fperiods and the odd passing shower.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FMainly dry with some sunny
OL,17,Fspells, but there will be a scattering
OL,18,Fof showers across the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
